<h1>Ruby on Rails — Auth Emails with Mailtrap</h1>
<p>This sample app demonstrates email verification and password reset using Devise + Mailtrap.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Register an account — a confirmation email is sent via Mailtrap</li>
  <li>Click the confirmation link to verify your email address</li>
  <li>Use "Forgot password" to receive a time-limited reset link</li>
  <li>Unconfirmed users cannot access protected pages</li>
</ul>

<% unless user_signed_in? %>
  <p>
    <%= link_to "Create an account", new_user_registration_path %> or
    <%= link_to "sign in", new_user_session_path %>
  </p>
<% end %>
